OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDrivers succeed in 100% of 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpenalty charge appeals     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, In one London borough drivers appealing
OL,6, against penalty charge notices were    
OL,7, successful every time for over a year. 
OL,9,FAfter I challenged a recent penalty    
OL,10,Fcharge, I found that from July 2022 to 
OL,11,FSeptember this year, Greenwich Council 
OL,12,Fdid not contest a single appeal -      
OL,13,Fciting "no evidence" in every instance.
OL,15,FIn such circumstance, the adjudicator  
OL,16,Fmust quash the driver's penalty charge.
OL,18,FGreenwich Council said it had not been 
OL,19,Fable to supply any evidence during that
OL,20,Fperiod because of staff shortages.     
